{"id":544275653,"lang":"cpp","time":"6 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1629939939,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"11 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/544275653/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"6 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int getval(char c){\n        if(c=='I') return 1;\n        else if(c=='V') return 5;\n        else if(c=='X') return 10;\n        else if(c=='L') return 50;\n        else if(c=='C') return 100;\n        else if(c=='D') return 500;\n        else return 1000;\n    }\n    int romanToInt(string s) {\n        int res =0;\n        for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){\n            int s1= getval(s[i]);\n            if(i+1<s.length()){\n               int s2= getval(s[i+1]);\n                if(s1>=s2)res+=s1;\n                else{\n                    res+=s2-s1;\n                    i++;\n                }\n            }\n            else res+=s1;\n        }\n        return res;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer"}
